(September 13, 1966) In the Matter of George Campbell Painting Corp. v. William Reid et al. George Campbell Painting Corp. v. William Reid et al.

Motions granted and the Attorney-General -of the State of New York is permitted to appear in this proceeding pursuant to section 71 of the Executive Law. Concur — Botein, P. J., Breitel, McNally, Steuer and Capozzoli, JJ.
